      "content": "the \"tapering\" thing sounds complicated and i'm not sure i can get an appointment soon. if my INR is already sitting perfectly in the middle of the range, wouldn't it be pretty safe to just jump to 2.5mg or 2mg for a bit to see how it goes? i really just want to know if it's actually dangerous to try a smaller dose since my levels are stable. can you just give me a straight answer on if a lower dose is okay given my stability?",
